Package org.pathvisio.libgpml.io

  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    PathwayModelExporter
    Interface for an exporter that writes a pathway to a file.

    Implemented by classes that can import a pathway from various different types.
    PathwayModelIO
    Common methods for PathwayModelImporters and PathwayModelExporters

    Class Description
    AbstractPathwayModelFormat
    base implementation of PathwayImporter and PathwayExporter warnings mechanism.
  • Exception Summary
    Exception Description
    ConverterException
    Exception that occurs during import, export, save or load of a pathway model.
